data.description: ***SELLERS WILLING TO OFFER CONCESSIONS TO LOWER BUYERS INTEREST RATE***.  Welcome home to this gorgeous and spacious single story home in Enchanted Lake. This home features a large kitchen with lots of cabinets and counter space, a large island, stainless steel appliances, and corian countertops. The primary bedroom has a spacious ensuite with a separate walk-in shower and jacuzzi tub for relaxing at the end of the day. Every room has a split AC unit, 8 in total in the entire home. If you are still working from home, then you will be thrilled with your new home office. The spacious sitting area, dining room, and family room with wet bar make entertaining a breeze, with enough space for everyone. There is a shaded covered patio, and a small front yard, with enough room for a vegetable garden, making lawn care easy and simple. There are even two custom made storage sheds for storing all of your beach and outdoor gear. This home also has 31 pre-paid leased photovoltaic panels to help lower those high Hawaiian electric bills. You're just one short mile from the Enchanted Lake Shopping center with several ono restaurants. Don't miss out on this beautiful home in Kailua.
